snippet.title: Recipe Tools
snippet.description: Tools for the recipe collector :-) RecipeFox: A addon to FireFox to grab recipes from the net (like the MasterCook addon in Internet Explorer) A recipe converter: It converts recipes from one format to another, and supports the following formats: - AccuC

snippet.title: JFreeChart
snippet.description: JFreeChart is a free (LGPL) chart library for the Java(tm) platform. It supports bar charts, pie charts, line charts, time series charts, scatter plots, histograms, simple Gantt charts, Pareto charts, bubble plots, dials, thermometers and more.

snippet.title: Brewtarget
snippet.description: Brewtarget is free brewing software for Linux, Mac, and Windows. Compatible with BeerSmith. Generates instructions for you from the recipe and interactive mash designer! Hit all your targets with brewtarget.

snippet.title: survey
snippet.description: Simple survey web application where an admin can create surveys with questions and activate questions one at a time. Users can answer the questions and see a pie chart with the current answers.

snippet.title: Gourmet
snippet.description: GNOME Recipe Manager w/ nutrition information and other useful plugins

snippet.title: Warzone 2100 Art Revolution
snippet.description: Art Revolution project for the Open Source real-time strategy game Warzone 2100, originally developed by Pumpkin studios and published by Eidos Interactive. This project aims to establish a new graphical quality level for the game as a whole.

snippet.title: v3c-launchpad
snippet.description: boostraps v3c recipe builds in launchpad
